"We have our very own website now!" → comment: "Damnnn I LOVE IT!!!" → {"tone_tags":["motivational","brotherhood"],"intent":"engagement-nurture","sales_stage":"nurture"}
"Biggest constraint in your coaching business" → comment: "lack of sales calls for my programs" → {"tone_tags":["motivational","hype","praise"],"intent":"objection-handling","sales_stage":"nurture"}

GENDER: infer from the author's first name. Use "male", "female", or "unknown".

Output: {"tone_tags":[...],"intent":"...","sales_stage":"...","gender":"male|female|unknown","reasoning":"one sentence"}

